# ✅ 10. Customer Loyalty (Repeat Rate)

```python
customer_orders = gold_df.groupBy("CustomerKey", "Continent") \
    .agg(F.countDistinct("Order Number").alias("order_count"))

repeat_customers = customer_orders.filter(F.col("order_count") >= 2)

kpi10 = customer_orders.groupBy("Continent").agg(
    (F.countDistinct(
        F.when(F.col("order_count") >= 2, F.col("CustomerKey"))
    ) / F.countDistinct("CustomerKey") * 100).alias("repeat_rate")
)

display(kpi10)
```

